{"tid":1188156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【非禮視障女童】「康橋之家」前院長張健華罪成判囚33個月 官斥令人髮指","createTime":"2019-06-06T05:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T05:38:27.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06338ca8df82e7b8d83dd910b472db3548294479","tid":1188156,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"私營殘疾院舍「康橋之家」前院長張健華，於1982年至1986年任職視障學校活動助理期間，在學校範圍及烏溪沙青年新村5度非禮一名患青光眼的視障女童，早前被裁定5項非禮罪罪成。練錦鴻暫委法官指事件令當時年僅7至12歲的女事主心理及精神受創傷，張健華利用其師長般的地位，多次在光天化日之下在公眾地方非禮事主，行為令人髮指，最終於區域法院被判囚33個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1017070-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE%E8%A6%96%E9%9A%9C%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E5%BA%B7%E6%A9%8B%E4%B9%8B%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%8D%E5%89%8D%E9%99%A2%E9%95%B7%E5%BC%B5%E5%81%A5%E8%8F%AF%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A33%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88+%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E9%AB%AE%E6%8C%87+\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1017070-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%259A%259C%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E3%2580%2591%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%2581%25A5%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A33%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%2B%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25AB%25AE%25E6%258C%2587%2B&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgjeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=f41799c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1017070-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%259A%259C%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E3%2580%2591%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25